description:
Yuri, a college student, is saved by Ouya Toshiomi, the young leader of the Ouya group when she&rsquo;s being forced into consuming illegal drugs at a party. Since then, even though she doesn&rsquo;t want to get involved with the internal dealings of the Yakuza, she can&rsquo;t help but fall for Toshiomi&rsquo;s surprisingly gentle smile. This is the story of two people who are attracted to each other, but the courtship of a man who lives staking his life may be too fierce and crazy&hellip; &ldquo;Yuri, it might be our last night, so let's get crazy together.&rdquo;
The most dangerous love ever, begins.

